title: 9-1-1 Episode 5 Review
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Just binged all your 911 reviews!!! I love this show so much, a lot of the things you say are very relatable. Like with buck and Abby’s relationship, at first I was like wtf also. But as they actually met in person I really saw a connection.
